@startuml pipeline_ensemble_prediction_modes
title PipelineEnsemble: режимы агрегации предсказаний

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

class PipelineEnsemble {
  +predict(input_data, output_mode)
  +finalize(validation_data)
  +select_best_models(validation_data, metric)
  -_predict_ensemble(...)
  -_aggregate_classification_predictions(...)
  -_compute_aggregation_weights(...)
  -_compute_model_weights(...)
  -_compute_base_routing_weights(...)
  -_compute_gated_weights(...)
}

class PipelineInfo {
  +name: partition name
  +pipeline: Pipeline
  +metrics: validation metrics
  +val_predictions
  +val_probabilities
}

class SamplingRoutingContext {
  +partition_names
  +base_weights(input_data, active_names)
  +transform_features(input_data)
}

class ConstrainedGatingRouter {
  +fit(features, prior_weights, predictions, target)
  +weights(features)
}

class "Chunk Pipeline" as ChunkPipeline {
  +predict(input_data, output_mode)
  +is_fitted
}

enum EnsembleMethod {
  voting
  weighted
  routed_weighted
  gated_weighted
}

PipelineEnsemble "1" *-- "many" PipelineInfo
PipelineInfo --> ChunkPipeline
PipelineEnsemble --> EnsembleMethod
PipelineEnsemble --> SamplingRoutingContext : routed/gated modes
PipelineEnsemble --> ConstrainedGatingRouter : gated_weighted

note right of PipelineEnsemble
  finalization:
  1. remove unfitted pipelines
  2. evaluate subsets on common validation data
  3. keep best subset
end note

note bottom of EnsembleMethod
  voting:
  regression = mean predictions
  classification = mean probabilities

  weighted:
  global weights from validation metrics

  routed_weighted:
  per-sample partition weights from Sampling Zoo predictor,
  combined with validation weights

  gated_weighted:
  learned per-sample weights from validation data,
  routing prior and pipeline predictions
end note

PipelineEnsemble --> PipelineInfo : requests predictions
PipelineEnsemble --> SamplingRoutingContext : base routing weights
SamplingRoutingContext --> "Sampling Zoo fitted strategy" : predict_partition_proba / predict_partitions / transform_embedding

@enduml
